						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Disch wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">So graphics are loaded and drawn at more or less the same speed...</div><br />Not only at the same speed, but also at the same TIME. As it fetches data for future pixels, it also draws pixels using data that was fetched before.</div>

